<br>
and again, even if you use a gamepad or macros, you cannot twist more than 3 songs effectively. 4 is a possibilty, but mostly you will  fail due to the dreaded &quot;start song/stop song&quot;-glitch or the lag-monster. also, using macros is especially bad when missing a note. <br>
